<h2 class=3D"wp-block-heading">WCPM Formula</h2>



<p>The following formula is used to calculate the total number of words cor=
rect per minute. </p><div id=3D"AdThrive_Content_3_tablet" class=3D"adthriv=
e-ad adthrive-sticky-container adthrive-content adthrive-content-3 adthrive=
-ad-cls"></div>



<div class=3D"wp-block-katex-display-block katex-eq katex-rendered" data-ka=
tex-display=3D"true"><span class=3D"katex-display"><span class=3D"katex"><s=
pan class=3D"katex-mathml"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathM=
L" display=3D"block"><semantics><mrow><mi>W</mi><mi>C</mi><mi>P</mi><mi>M</=
mi><mo>=3D</mo><mo stretchy=3D"false">[</mo><mi>T</mi><mi>W</mi><mo>=E2=88=
=92</mo><mi>M</mi><mo stretchy=3D"false">]</mo><mi mathvariant=3D"normal">/=
</mi><mi>T</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">WCPM =3D [=
TW - M] / T</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=3D"katex-html=
" aria-hidden=3D"true"><span class=3D"base"><span class=3D"strut" style=3D"=
height: 0.6833em;"></span><span class=3D"mord mathnormal" style=3D"margin-r=
ight: 0.1389em;">W</span><span class=3D"mord mathnormal" style=3D"margin-ri=
ght: 0.109em;">CPM</span><span class=3D"mspace" style=3D"margin-right: 0.27=
78em;"></span><span class=3D"mrel">=3D</span><span class=3D"mspace" style=
=3D"margin-right: 0.2778em;"></span></span><span class=3D"base"><span class=
=3D"strut" style=3D"height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;"></span><span cla=
ss=3D"mopen">[</span><span class=3D"mord mathnormal" style=3D"margin-right:=
 0.1389em;">T</span><span class=3D"mord mathnormal" style=3D"margin-right: =
0.1389em;">W</span><span class=3D"mspace" style=3D"margin-right: 0.2222em;"=
></span><span class=3D"mbin">=E2=88=92</span><span class=3D"mspace" style=
=3D"margin-right: 0.2222em;"></span></span><span class=3D"base"><span class=
